{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-express-disagreement/task-103","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-express-disagreement","challengeType":19,"description":"","nodules":null,"explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Split into parts</span> znači podeliti nešto na delove. Na primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">When working on a large project, it's helpful to split it into parts to make it more manageable.</span> – To znači podeliti veliki zadatak ili projekat na manje delove kojima je lakše upravljati.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">To understand the problem better, let's split the problem into parts and address each one.</span> – Ovo znači razložiti problem na manje delove kako bi se lakše pronašlo rešenje.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Anna predlaže da umesto izbora između tehnologije ili nameštaja za kancelarije, podijele stipendiju kako bi se koristila za oba.</p>\n</section>","helpCategory":"English","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušajte audio odgovor na pitanje ispod.</p>\n</section>","fields":{"slug":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-express-disagreement/task-103"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Šta predlaže Ana?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Kutoa stipendio kabisa.</p>","feedback":"<p>Anna hapendekezi kuondoa stipendio.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Podela stipendije na dva dela.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Korišćenje stipendije isključivo za kancelarijski nameštaj.</p>","feedback":"<p>Anna anapendekeza suluhisho la wastani, si kuchagua upande mmoja.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Povećanje stipendije za sve.</p>","feedback":"<p>Anna hakutaja kuongeza kiasi.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":2}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company1-boardroom.png","charact